Ancient amulet
Dartas said he saw a trinket that could help open the entrance to a cave in the valley of the Two Rivers. This amulet was found by the headman of a village not far from Dar-Leanos. Now this village has been inhabited by harpies, and the cause of this most likely lies in the amulet.
#subobj 1
Come to the village
The destroyed village where the starosta, the finder of the old amulet, lived is located west of the city.
#subobj 2
Take the amulet
Most likely the old amulet lies in the old man's trunk.